  <member name="T:SemanticVersion">
    <summary>
    Hedera follows semantic versioning () for both the HAPI protobufs and
    the Services software. This type allows the getVersionInfo query in the
    NetworkService to return the deployed versions of both protobufs and
    software on the node answering the query.
    
    See <a href="https://docs.hedera.com/guides/docs/hedera-api/basic-types/semanticversion">Hedera Documentation</a></summary>
  </member>
  <member name="F:SemanticVersion.Major">
    <summary>
    Increases with incompatible API changes
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="M:SemanticVersion.#ctor(System.Int32,System.Int32,System.Int32)">
    <summary>
    Increases with backwards-compatible new functionality
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="M:SemanticVersion.#ctor(System.Int32,System.Int32,System.Int32)_2">
    <summary>
    Increases with backwards-compatible bug fixes
